homedefaultJson.title: Michael Wittorp
homedefaultJson.description: My name is Michael Wittorp. A highly motivated, uplifting, and inspirational software developer.
homedefaultJson.subtitle: Software Engineer & Web Developer
homedefaultJson.description2: I am highly-skilled in web development, database management, and backend programming. I am interested in seeing where the future will take us, and am thankful to be in the forefront of technology. I am excited about autonomous self-driving cars, virtual reality, space exploration, machine learning, game development, beautiful computer applications, fantasy science fiction, and theme parks.
